 Language Translation App
🚀 A simple and interactive language translation app built with Gradio, Google Translator API, and gTTS for speech synthesis.

Live Link :"https://huggingface.co/spaces/Thilak118/LanguageTranslation"

✨ Features
✅ Translate text into multiple languages
✅ Auto-detect input language
✅ Generate speech output for supported languages
✅ User-friendly interface with Gradio

🚀 Deploying on Hugging Face Spaces
1️⃣ Create a new Hugging Face Space
2️⃣ Set SDK type to Gradio
3️⃣ Upload app.py, requirements.txt, and language.csv
4️⃣ Run the app and make your Space public

🎯 How to Use
1️⃣ Enter the text you want to translate
2️⃣ Select the target language
3️⃣ Click Translate
4️⃣ Listen to the translated speech output (if supported)

🛠️ Technologies Used
🔹 Python
🔹 Gradio (UI framework)
🔹 Google Translator API (Translation)
🔹 gTTS (Text-to-Speech)
🔹 Pandas (Data Handling)

